import React from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper, IconButton, Tooltip, Link } from '@mui/material'; import RestoreIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Restore'; import DeleteIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Delete'; import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles'; const StyledTableCell = styled(TableCell)(({ theme }) => ({ '&.MuiTableCell-head': { backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === 'dark' ? '#1e1e1e' : '#f5f5f5', fontWeight: 600 } })); const SearchHistory = ({ history, onRestoreSearch, onDeleteSearch }) => { return ( Siste søk {history.map((item) => ( {item.course_name} {new Date(item.created_at).toLocaleString('nb-NO')} onRestoreSearch(item)}> onDeleteSearch(item.id)}> Kurs Studiepoeng Likhet {item.results?.slice(0, 5).map((result) => ( {result.kurskode} {result.kursnavn} {result.credits} result.similarity >= 70 ? theme.palette.success.main : result.similarity >= 50 ? theme.palette.warning.main : theme.palette.error.main }} > {result.similarity}% ))}
))} ); }; export default SearchHistory;
